<div class="container my-4">
  <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>
  <p>This application uses data from the following sources:</p>
  <ul class="list-group mb-4">
    <li class="list-group-item">CSV files for shelters, tags, and pets</li>
    <li class="list-group-item">Petfinder API for additional shelters and pets data</li>
    <li class="list-group-item">Faker Gems for additional shelters, tags, and pets</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Our ERD (Entity-Relationship Diagram) is as follows:</p>
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <%= image_tag 'erd.png', alt: 'ERD', class: 'img-fluid' %>
